'''Coal''' is the highest paying cargo at the start of the game and is delivered straight from [[Main/en/Coal Mine]] to [[Main/en/Power Station]] without the need for any intermediate processing, enabling very simple connecting routes.



==Strategies==
Coal is often used as a money maker at the start of games, especially in ''#openttdcoop'' games that use it exclusively until they begin building the actual network.

